# Udacity_FEND_P2
Animal Trading Card

This project consisted of a prototype of an animal trading card. I utilized HTML and CSS displaying my growth of research and applying multiple elements to create the trading card. To conclude, I applied border style, measurements for width, height, margin, padding, background color, font weight, page wrap, and container.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
